This is a bomb-defuse adventure. Terrorists are settled in a small village. In the late afternoon, the counter-terrorists are trying to take control of this place and every supplies located here, at the top of the cliff on the southern Brittany coast.

V1 : Waypoints included in the .bsp

This is a complete creation from a CS1.6 map made by Atomfried.
The new V2 is located here :



I hope that you'll enjoy the adventure, and you'll propose me as much coms as you want to optimise the real incoming work.
Thanks a lot to all of you, and for your vote !
